   "id": "cell-07-bias-math",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## The Root Cause: LLM Judges Are Systematically Biased\n",
    "\n",
    "On the 100 conversations where both human and judge labels are available, the gap is clear: the judge consistently under-reports hallucinations.\n",
    "\n",
    "GLIDE's **PPI rectifier** measures this systematic error on the labeled subset, then applies the correction to the remaining 900 conversations:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\hat{\\mu}_{\\text{PPI}} = \\underbrace{\\bar{y}_{\\text{proxy}}^{\\,(N)}}_\\text{cheap signal} + \\underbrace{\\left(\\bar{y}_{\\text{true}} - \\bar{y}_{\\text{proxy}}^{\\,(n)}\\right)}_\\text{rectifier}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "The rectifier ($\\bar{y}_{\\text{true}} - \\bar{y}_{\\text{proxy}}$) equals zero when the judge is perfectly calibrated and grows large when the judge is biased — exactly the situation here."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 31,
   "id": "cell-08-bias-chart",
   "metadata": {
